summary:
- **New class action filed** against N.M. Super and AMP Superannuation (ASL) related to alleged higher life insurance premiums (2019-2024). AMP entities will defend.  
- **Separate legal proceeding** by Dexus against AMP entities (Collimate Capital, AMP Group Holdings) over Macquarie Shopping Centre sale dispute. AMP will defend.  

*No material financial, operational, or trading implications disclosed (defence stance only).*
